                         The main obligations of the
                        Linear Collider Physics Group
                                    are:

   [blueball_t.gif] Assessment of the physics capabilities of a linear
       collider and their dependence on the collider parameters;

   [blueball_t.gif] Understanding of linear collider contributions to the
       world high energy physics program in the LHC era;

   If you are interested in joining the study please contact
   Andreas Kronfeld or Slawek Tkaczyk or both.
